{"name":"德川家光","nameCn":"","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/c0/2e/2207_crt_Mldrm.jpg","info":"<li><span>别名: </span>德川家光</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>とくがわ いえみつ</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Tokugawa Iemitsu</li><li><span>性别: </span>男</li><li><span>生日: </span>1604-08-12</li><li><span>卒日: </span>1651-06-08</li>","detail":"德川幕府第三代将军。二代将军德川秀忠次子，母为崇源院（浅井江），自小由乳母春日局抚养。弟弟忠长更得父母喜爱，企图争位，遭到德川家康制止。家光即位后进行报复，逼迫忠长自杀。<br />家光在位期间，重用春日局、柳生宗矩、松平信纲等亲信，强化将军权威，落实幕藩体制、强化锁国令、加大天主教镇压力度，基本完成幕府体制构建。<br />家光虽建立后宫大奥体制，但无子，死后发生继承危机。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/30391","name":"葵 徳川三代","nameCn":"葵 德川三代","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/c3/be/30391_Aj50n.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":6},{"href":"/subject/50036","name":"大奥～誕生 [有功・家光篇]","nameCn":"大奥~诞生[有功・家光篇]","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/9f/75/50036_Bxgb8.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":6},{"href":"/subject/8753","name":"大奥〜第一章〜","nameCn":"大奥第一章","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/48/c8/8753_Nv1NC.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":6},{"href":"/subject/94518","name":"春日局","nameCn":"春日局","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/4c/32/94518_6M701.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"江口洋介","castHref":"/person/19960","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/c6/f3/19960_prsn_0hg4L.jpg","type":6}]}